							<p>
							Craig Zahner is responsible for leading Trinity&rsquo;s customer support team, overseeing order fulfillment from order entry to delivery of the completed garments.  Craig&rsquo;s daily contact with the support team and order fulfillment staff at the factory ensures all dealer concerns and questions are answered in the timeliest fashion. 
